## Orkish programming language guide

### Translated glossary 

Syntax is always updated for more accurate Orkish.

| Orkish           | English        |
|------------------|----------------|
| shal             | in             |
| ukeav            | set            |
| ukhow            | print          |
| ro               | of             |
| wiavh            | with           |
| katu             | here           |
| iuk              | is             |
| avhem            | them           |
| agh              | and            |
| mubarum          | end            |
| bugd             | call           |
| ukavrucav        | struct         |
| geav             | get            |
| eiavhas          | either         |
| ukpliav          | split          |
| nauk-gex         | regex          |
| avrue            | true           |
| faluke           | false          |
| noav             | not            |
| maavch           | match          |
| lefav            | left           |
| righav           | right          |
| brackeav         | bracket        |
| differenav       | not equal      |
| um               | if             |
| avhan            | than           |
| leukuk           | less           |
| greaavas         | greater        |
| pluuk            | plus           |
| minuuk           | minus          |
| mulavippak       | multiply       |
| diviukion        | division       |
| eluke            | else           |
| nauk-peaav       | repeat         |
| duraumn          | during         |
| julavil          | until          |
| ukavarav         | start          |
| nauk-avurn       | return         |
| aceukuk          | acess          |
| incremenav       | increment      |
| enumeraave       | enumerate      |
| creaave          | create         |

### Hello world

```
shal hello ukeav "hello world".

ukhow hello.
```
hello world

Not allowed empty variable assignment.

Typing is dynamic.

### Procedures

#### Declaration

```
katu iuk HelloWorld avhem
shal hello ukeav "hello world" agh ukhow hello mubarum
```

#### Apply

```
bugd HelloWorld.
```

#### Recursive

```
katu iuk HelloWorld avhem ukhow hello agh bugd HelloWorld mubarum
```

### Objects

#### Declaration

```
ukavrucav Obj avhem var1 var2 var3 mubarum
```

#### Acess

```
ro Obj geav var1.
```

#### Assignment

```
ro Obj geav var1 ukeav 0.
```

### Strings

#### RegExp

```
"Hello World" ukpliav nauk-gex /[ ]/g.
```

### Logical expr

#### And

```
avrue agh faluke.
```
faluke

#### Or

```
avrue eiavhas faluke.
```
avrue

#### Not

```
noav avrue.
```
faluke

#### Equal to

```
avrue maavch wiavh faluke.
```
faluke

#### Not equal

```
avrue differenav ro faluke.
```
avrue

#### Less than

```
1 leukuk avhan 2.
```
avrue

#### Greater than

```
2 greaavas avhan 1.
```
avrue

#### Greater than or equal to

```
2 greaavas avhan eiavhas maavch wiavh 2.
```
avrue

#### Less than or equal to

```
1 leukuk avhan eiavhas maavch wiavh 2.
```
avrue

### Math expr

#### Plus

```
1 pluuk 1.
```
2

#### Minus

```
2 minuuk 1.
```
1

#### Multiply

```
2 mulavippak 2.
```
4

#### Division

```
4 diviukion 2.
```
2

### Conditionals 

#### if

```
um lefav brackeav avrue differenav ro faluke 
righav brackeav avhem ukhow hello mubarum
```

#### if... else

```
um lefav brackeav avrue differenav ro faluke 
righav brackeav avhem ukhow hello eluke avhem ukhow hello mubarum
```

### Loop

#### While 

```
nauk-peaav avrue avhem ukhow hello mubarum
```

#### For

```
duraumn shal I ukeav 1 julavil 2 avhem ukhow hello mubarum
```